Laura_Kenny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Kenny\"}, {\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999997862307966, \"rank\": 2.1347020808563305e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 305, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999980925358616, \"rank\": 1.9074547218274596e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"motherhood\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"that extra motivation\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the most dominant dressage riders of her era, Dujardin travels to France already with six Olympic medals and three golds to her name, writing herself into British sporting folklore.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9483276326030009, \"rank\": 0.044038489847321616, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999941737082059, \"rank\": 3.64670161410178e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most dominant dressage riders\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"her era\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"six Olympic medals\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"three golds\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kenny,who retired earlier this year, also owns six medals with five of them gold but could be eclipsed by Dujardin, who has strong hopes in both the individual and team dressage competitions.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kenny\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"six medals\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"strong hopes\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"both the individual and team dressage competitions\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But as a new mother, giving birth to Isabella in March 2023, she possesses a whole new source of drive as she seeks to make her baby girl proud and take Kenny's crown at the pinnacle of British sport.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 762, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isabella_of_France\", \"score\": 0.6988923979093947, \"rank\": 0.30001473326570155, \"text\": \"Isabella\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isabella_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isabella_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999941737082059, \"rank\": 3.64670161410178e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new mother\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole new source\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"drive\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"her baby girl\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"Kenny's crown\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"the pinnacle\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think in a way it does push me more because obviously I want to make her proud,\\\" said Dujardin, 38.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City AM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"The Turnover\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"your weekly roundup\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"sport business news\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"City AM's sports desk\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very well driven and I am always out there to succeed and bring back some medals if I can.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some medals\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd never go down without a fight, and to have my little girl there is really, really special.\\\"\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fight\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"my little girl\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With history beckoning atChateau de Versailles, where the Paris 2024 Olympic dressagewill be held, it's vital that Dujardin does not let the heightened expectations get to her.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1416, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"score\": 0.99997893102117, \"rank\": 2.1069422768061337e-05, \"text\": \"Versailles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palace_of_Versailles\"}, {\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.936643998235428e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"the heightened expectations\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in full knowledge of how to succeed on the big stage, she is hardly feeling the pressure - opening up on her secret to success.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"full knowledge\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1584}, {\"ngram\": \"the big stage\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure - opening\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"her secret\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know it's an Olympics and it's obviously a huge honour to be going to represent a country, but I always just look at it as another competition,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge honour\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"a country\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"another competition\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know if this is a crazy thing to say.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crazy thing\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just do exactly the same as what I do all the time, so do not try and make it more than it is.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I can bring back some medals, which I will for sure be out there to be doing, then fantastic.\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some medals\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if not, it will be back to the drawing board and work a bit harder and see what I can do another year.\\\"\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the drawing board\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dujardin is one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sport's National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing them to train full time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2257, \"end\": 2265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 2257, \"end\": 2265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"over 1,000 elite athletes\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2253}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is vital for her pathway to the Paris 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her pathway\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Games\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While securing two bronze medals in the individual and team events in Tokyo, her last Olympic experience was slightly tainted bythe lack of fans or family present, due to the Covid-19 pandemic.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2560, \"end\": 2565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999737096917, \"rank\": 2.6265757956742657e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two bronze medals\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual and team events\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"her last Olympic experience\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2634}, {\"ngram\": \"family present\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2652}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This came after Rio 2016, which again lacked much of a partisan British faithful due to the outbreak of Zika virus.\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999975166600874, \"rank\": 2.4833461885719e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2749, \"end\": 2756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999941737082059, \"rank\": 3.64670161410178e-05, \"text\