", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fantastic Olympics\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"Zika virus\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody really wanted to travel to Rio so we did not really have friends and family come out, we did not really have many spectators.\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3065, \"end\": 3068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999975166600874, \"rank\": 2.4833461885719e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3113}, {\"ngram\": \"many spectators\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then there was Covid in Tokyo, so we have had two Olympics which have had no spectators and no atmosphere.\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3194, \"end\": 3199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999737096917, \"rank\": 2.6265757956742657e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"two Olympics\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3228}, {\"ngram\": \"no spectators\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"no atmosphere\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just been us.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now all of a sudden we are going to have that whole support back and be there with the crowds and everything.\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that whole support\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3357}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be fantastic.\\\"\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"National Lottery players raise more than \\u00a330million a week for good causes including vital funding into sport - from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3438, \"end\": 3454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999998880030097, \"rank\": 1.1199362342481725e-07, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good causes\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3512}, {\"ngram\": \"vital funding\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3536}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"grassroots\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"elite\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To find out more visit:www.lotterygoodcauses.org.uk#TNLAthletes Share this article Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more visit\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3598}, {\"ngram\": \"this article\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3658}, {\"ngram\": \"the City AM newsletter\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3694}, {\"ngram\": \"o